data.title: Made In Austin (Film & Television)
data.meta_description: Austin has a rich history in film and television productions. The Austin Film Commission has a comprehensive filmography including award winning indies and large budget studio productions made in Austin over the past 50 years.
data.text:
MADE IN AUSTIN

Austin has amassed a rich history of locally made films and television series over the past five decades. The homegrown scene grew from a handful of regional productions into a full-on independent movement that is admired around the world. Thanks to many renowned and distinctive voices, a talented crew base and diverse locations, Austin's eclectic filmography features a mix of award-winning indies, large budget studio productions and original network television series.
